p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1BHK Flat Interior Design Cost in Kolkata<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The cost of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/1bhk-interior-design\/\">transforming a 1 BHK flat<\/a> in Kolkata involves various factors like carpet area, materials, finishes, and design styles. For spaces ranging from 250-450 sq. ft., the investment typically falls between 3 to 4 Lakh. Many homeowners prefer minimalistic, simple designs for a more affordable option, choosing light colour tones to create a spacious feel. Covered storage units and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/space-saving-design\/\">space-saving designs<\/a> are popular choices.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150151\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata.jpg\" alt=\"1 BHK interior design cost in Kolkata\" class=\"wp-image-55254\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150151\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150151\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150151\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150151\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150151\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">1BHK Flat interior design in Kolkata<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2BHK Interior Design Cost in Kolkata<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A stylish 2BHK home interior project in Kolkata comes in the 6-7 Lakhs price range. For those with a penchant for luxury, a lavish <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/2bhk-interior-design\/\">2 BHK interior design<\/a> in Kolkata may range from 10-14 Lakhs.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The basic home interior furniture includes a queen bed, cupboards, a modular kitchen with base and overhead cabinets, and a minimalistic crockery unit. You can upgrade your 2BHK space with a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-island-designs-for-home\/\">kitchen island<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wall-mounted-murphy-bed-designs\/\">Murphy bed<\/a>, and personalised bed designs, among many other design options. (DesignCafe offers <strong>51,041 design possibilities<\/strong>.) Homeowners can choose from basic, semi-premium, or premium materials, depending on their preferences. For example, a wardrobe with a basic matte finish would be cheaper than an Italian finish.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Young couples sometimes turn their second bedroom into a multifunctional room, so the prices may soar if you opt for space-saving solutions like a Murphy bed (Foldable space-saving bed).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150142\/2-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata.jpg\" alt=\"2 BHK interior design cost in Kolkata\" class=\"wp-image-55253\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150142\/2-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150142\/2-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150142\/2-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150142\/2-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150142\/2-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">2 BHK Interior design cost in Kolkata<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Revive your home with modern and affordable home interiors!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/09144537\/revive-your-home-with-modern-and-affordable-home-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3BHK Interior Design Cost in Kolkata<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A basic <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/3bhk-interior-design\/\">3BHK interior design<\/a> in Kolkata will range from 7-8.5 Lakhs, while semi-premium and premium options can go up to 11-14 Lakhs. Homeowners usually opt for high-end options like glass shutters for cabinets, luxurious finishes, extravagant <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/different-types-of-false-ceiling-designs\/\">false ceiling designs<\/a>, additional furniture like a tall unit, multifunctional partitions, etc.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>DesignCafe has its own in-house 65,000 sq. ft factory with quality materials for every budget.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Aria finishes &#8211; Clients looking for pocket-friendly rates<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Nova finishes &#8211; Most common and semi-premium<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Abetti premium &#8211; semi-premium to high-end<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Signature finishes\/ Premium finishes &#8211; High-end packages<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/31150133\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-kolkata.jpg\" alt=\"3 BHK interior design cost in Kolkata\" class=\"wp-image-55252\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-