ner regarding aesthetic preferences.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. How much does a 4BHK interior designer cost in Kolkata?<\/strong><br>For a 4BHK interior design project in Kolkata, the cost typically starts from 7.5 lakhs and may vary based on specific design requirements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. How much does it cost to renovate a flat in Kolkata?<\/strong><br>Flat renovation costs in Kolkata can vary, but typically,&nbsp; the average home interior costs start at 4 lacs, and there are civil costs based on the client&#8217;s current status of interiors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. How much does a villa interior design cost in Kolkata?<\/strong><br>Villa interior design costs in Kolkata generally start from 15 lakhs and can increase based on the villa&#8217;s carpet area and specific design preferences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-mini